data.description: Welcome home to 3120 Miller Street! This 3-bedroom, 1 bath home in Port Richmond boasts beautiful original details. Enter into the large living room with high ceilings and knotty pine wide plank hardwood floors throughout. Flow through to the nice sized dining room, great for entertaining friends and family and continue to the eat-in kitchen and extra seating at the counter. Make your way outside to the spacious rear yard with semi-covered patio, great for barbecuing and gardening! The second floor has 3 bedrooms as well plus a full hall bathroom with skylight and hallway closet. The full finished basement includes a laundry area with plenty of room for storage and a half bathroom. A new heater and central air conditioning unit was installed 7-2023! This home is steps from Campbell Square Park, Gaul & Co. Malt House, New Wave Cafe, Lunar Inn and River Wards Cafe. Don't forget Taconelli's Pizza! You will also have easy access to Fishtown, grocery stores, Target, Home Depot, Lowe's, Planet Fitness and is just minutes to I-95 and Delaware Ave!
